ЯР'], 'source': 'https://armyinform.com.ua/2023/04/11/nashi-muzhni-voyiny-8-j-misyacz-strymuyut-rosarmiyu-u-bahmuti-vid-prosuvannya-vglyb-ganna-malyar/'}